description:
Twilight Sparkle has been looking forward to family bowling night with her parents, Shining Armor, and Cadence. But as she's about to leave, Princess Celestia gives her an urgent mission. How will she be able to balance both work and family fun time? Get comfy and find out!
https://www.patreon.com/Tamers12345
https://x.com/TheTamers12345

Dear Teamers

I love your pony videos, and your Sonic Underground continuation. Your absurd humor and amazing storytelling brings joy to an anguished world, like aloe vera on a burnt anus. I was there for derpygate, I was there for down with molestia, and I was there for the aryanne fiasco at derpibooru. I heard your last video got flagged and I am worried that you might be in the crosshairs of yet another killjoy. 

Is there a repository anywhere to download your pony videos so they are not lost forever?
